---
layout: base.njk
title: Nathan Kling
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="hero__name">Nathan Kling</h1>
    <p class="hero__tagline">Turning AI ambition into organizational reality.<br>Strategy. Transformation. Delivery.</p>
    <a href="mailto:nathan@thinkingmanagement.com" class="btn">Let's Talk</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title">About</h2>
    <div class="about__content">
      <p class="about__lead">I help organizations stop experimenting with AI and start executing.</p>
      <p>Over fifteen years leading professional services teams, delivering complex programs, and driving organizational change — the kind that survives first contact with reality. I've built and scaled delivery organizations, led enterprise transformations, and now focus on the gap most companies can't close: turning AI strategy into operational capability.</p>
      <p>The hard part isn't the technology. It's the leadership alignment, the capability building, the change management that separates a pilot from a practice. That's where I work.</p>
      <p>MBA and Master of Music — analytical rigor meets creative problem-solving. I think in systems, communicate in stories, and ship on deadlines.</p>
      <div class="about__availability">
        <h3>Open to</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Executive leadership roles</li>
          <li>Fractional / interim engagements</li>
          <li>Advisory &amp; board positions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="writing" class="writing">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title">Writing</h2>
    <p class="section__subtitle">Thoughts on AI adoption, leadership, and the human side of transformation.</p>
    <div class="articles">
      {%- for article in articles %}
      <article class="article-card">
        <span class="article-card__source">{{ article.source }}</span>
        <time class="article-card__date" datetime="{{ article.date }}">{{ article.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <h3 class="article-card__title">
          <a href="{{ article.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ article.title }}</a>
        </h3>
        <p class="article-card__excerpt">{{ article.excerpt }}</p>
      </article>
      {%- endfor %}
      {%- if articles.length == 0 %}
      <p class="articles__empty">New writing coming soon.</p>
      {%- endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section__title">Get in Touch</h2>
    <p class="contact__lead">Interested in working together? Let's start a conversation.</p>
    <div class="contact__links">
      <a href="mailto:nathan@thinkingmanagement.com" class="contact__link">
        <span class="contact__label">Email</span>
        <span class="contact__value">nathan@thinkingmanagement.com</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/nathankling" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact__link">
        <span class="contact__label">LinkedIn</span>
        <span class="contact__value">linkedin.com/in/nathankling</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
